These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, lilac
2 different games are played: bridge, monopoly
1. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Color   | lilac  | grey |
| Game       | bridge | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different games are played: whist, billiard
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Game   | whist | billiard |
| Movie-Genre      | western     | thriller  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
City: san-francisco, colone
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, october
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| City   | san-francisco | colone  |
| Birthday   | december | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
